Refactor HomePage and Dashboard components for improved functionality and UI

- Integrated location selection with state and city dropdowns in HomePage, enhancing user experience for address input.
- Updated search functionality to redirect users to the buscar page with query parameters based on selected location and guest count.
- Enhanced Dashboard layout to display user plan information more clearly, including active plan details and current usage.
- Added rejection reason handling in BookingDetailPage for declined bookings, improving communication with clients.
- Updated AddressSearch component to support state and city selection with improved loading states and dropdown functionality.
- Masked sensitive contact information in PostCard component to enhance privacy.
